      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of conditions represented in the COU, including at least two loading rates or environmental conditions.",
      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single crosshead displacement rate (5 mm/min) and ambient temperature only. A second loading rate or physiological temperature condition was not included. This factor is below the required level; the gap is accepted given that quasi-static rate insensitivity of Ti-6Al-4V has been established in prior literature, and a compensating safety factor is applied."
