    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/depuy-synthes-vv40-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test Conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted on the basis of documented rate insensitivity of Ti-6Al-4V under quasi-static loading and the application of a compensating safety factor. All quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, relative error < 10%) are satisfied across all QoIs and both test laboratories. The overall credibility profile is sufficient to support the Medium assurance level required for a Class II device with Medium model influence and Medium decision consequence.",
